1
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:49,960
General

2
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:50,680
General

3
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:01,520
So lively today, huh?

4
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,680
Why didn't you invite Sis Fei too?

5
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:04,720
Sis Fei

6
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:06,320
Don't forget...

7
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:08,240
Hong Ye is my blood uncle.

8
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:10,320
You sure you wanna get involved in this?

9
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,480
Then what if...

10
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,840
I insist on getting involved?

11
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,720
Can you protect him forever?

12
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,360
Debts in Dongba...

13
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,840
...are paid in blood.

14
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:41,840
Thank you, General.

15
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:42,760
Take care, General.

16
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,520
Dawa...

17
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,640
...won't just let this go.

18
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,520
Then I'll see this through to the end.

19
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,000
Come stay at my place for a couple of days.

20
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,800
He won't dare enter my turf for now.

21
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:02,880
I can protect you...

22
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,760
...and your restaurant.

23
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,280
Okay.

24
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,400
Xingchen Ge.

25
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,320
We've got a huge problem!

26
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,760
Ms. Xingyu went to Dongba all alone...

27
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,200
...to investigate Wu Di's death.

28
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,200
This is ridiculous!

29
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,880
Deploy the security team immediately.

30
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,440
Bring Xingyu back safe, no matter what.

31
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,120
Okay.

32
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,640
Xingyu, Xingyu...

33
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:38,720
With you stirring things up like this...

34
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,520
...how am I supposed to play my next move?

35
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:01,040
See all this decadence?

36
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,200
Smell the money...

37
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,160
...and the scent of desire?

38
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,640
Stick with me.

39
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,560
Everything here...

40
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:11,920
Money.

41
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:13,680
Status.

42
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,120
Women.

43
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,280
It can all be yours.

44
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,320
Sis Fei...

45
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,680
I'm afraid these hands of mine...

46
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,640
...can't hold a prize this big.

47
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,400
Quit messing with me.

48
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,400
My word is gold.

49
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:36,880
Just wait.

50
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,400
Search every single house!

51
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,600
Find A-Di and that bitch!

52
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:53,160
Block every exit!

53
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,280
We must catch them tonight!

54
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,440
What the hell are you doing?

55
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,360
Is this a place for a waiter like you?

56
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:32,960
You looking for trouble?

57
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,360
Where's Sis Fei?

58
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,800
She told me to take over this nightclub.

59
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,400
What?

60
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,280
Let you take over?

61
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,560
Did you lick Sis Fei's boots?

62
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,840
When I was risking my life with Sis Fei...

63
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:49,000
...you were still in diapers.

64
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,480
You wanna sit in this seat?

65
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,600
Dream on!

66
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,120
Brother Kun's right.

67
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,280
Sis Fei would actually choose you...

68
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,960
...a guy who reeks of slop?

69
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:59,040
You'd better crawl back to your doghouse.

70
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,640
And stop embarrassing yourself here.

71
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,920
Maybe he really has something special.

72
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,560
Like he's really good at licking.

73
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:09,080
Either way, Sis Fei said it.

74
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,000
Believe it or not.

75
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,200
I can't be bothered to explain.

76
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:15,960
You think Sis Fei would say that to trash like you?

77
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,080
I've been with Sis Fei for years.

78
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,080
If anyone gets this spot, it's me...

79
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:21,040
...not some irrelevant outsider like you.

80
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:22,520
Get lost!

81
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,280
Get the hell out!

82
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,760
If you don't get out now, I'll show you...

83
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,400
...how Dongba takes out the trash.

84
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,320
Stop!

85
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,080
Sis!

86
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,160
He came to cause trouble, so I was kicking him out!

87
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:40,720
This is the contract.

88
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,560
Effective once signed.

89
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,000
From now on...

90
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,200
...he's the one calling the shots here.

91
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:46,920
Sis Fei...

92
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,000
You're serious?

93
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:51,280
I came mainly to thank you for bailing me out.

94
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,200
Otherwise...

95
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,680
...dealing with that Dawa guy...

96
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,840
...would've been a real pain.

97
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,560
Leave us.

98
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,920
The more I look at you, the more you look like my husband.

99
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,440
You really get me worked up.

100
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,880
If you wanna leave...

101
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,320
...that's fine.

102
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:20,240
But you have to give me a chance to thank you.

103
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:23,600
I'll show you what the nightlife here is really like.

104
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,720
Have some real fun tonight.

105
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,360
If you try to refuse again...

106
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,480
...you're disrespecting me.

107
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,640
Since you're so generous, Sis...

108
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,240
Then I won't hold back.

109
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,680
You two, take good care of A-Di.

110
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,800
If you can make him never want to leave...

111
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,800
...that'd be perfect.

112
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:08,760
Sis...

113
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,680
There's something off about that kid.

114
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,360
He offended Dawa today...

115
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,800
...tomorrow he could sell us out.

116
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,640
He's just a waiter dumping slop.

117
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,400
How can we hand the club over to him?

118
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,720
Mind your own turf.

119
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,880
What kind of person A-Di is...

120
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,720
...I know better than you.

121
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,840
I need him to deal with that rabid dog Dawa.

122
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,120
This is the first time you've questioned me...

123
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,040
...and it'll be the last.

124
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,000
Boy!

125
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:37,400
I'll make sure you die in pieces!

126
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:44,240
Stop right there!

127
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:45,680
Turn around.

128
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,320
Get in the car!

129
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,000
Chase them!

130
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,800
Thanks, ladies.

131
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,360
(Dawa is at the Lical Hotel. Go take him out.)

132
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,600
Thank you, General.

133
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,440
Take care, General.

134
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,320
General Dawa.

135
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,760
Please look after me from now on.

136
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,600
Thanks for taking care of me.

137
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,880
From now on in Dongba...

138
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,880
Dawa is dead.

139
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:23,880
Yeah.

140
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,320
A long-range one-shot kill.

141
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:29,080
A 7.62x51mm NATO sniper round.

142
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,880
Hit the temple dead-on.

143
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,160
After ballistic calculations,

144
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:34,680
the shot was from over 1,200 meters away.

145
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:37,360
Where's A-Di?

146
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,000
Still inside. Everything's normal.

147
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:39,960
Let's go.

148
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,240
Come with me and take a look.

149
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:42,320
Sis.

150
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,120
Going in right now

151
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:46,640
isn't a good idea, is it?

152
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,520
Kick that door and I'll break your leg.

153
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:58,800
Dawa is dead.

154
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,800
So I can go back now, right?

155
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:07,960
Forget it.

156
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,640
I wanna stay one more night too.

157
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:10,920
We'll head back tomorrow.

158
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,160
Then do whatever you want.

159
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,960
As long as you're having fun,

160
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,680
you can stay as long as you want.

161
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:35,400
Good thing it was just a decoy tonight.

162
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,960
You actually wanted to kill me.

163
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:44,880
Just wait.

164
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,680
I'll give you a surprise.

165
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:08,640
Why'd you save me?

166
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,600
That's my place too.

167
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,880
Those goons are like flies,

168
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,440
swarming my door to block you.

169
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,920
I saw it, so I gave you a hand.

170
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,000
Isn't that normal?

171
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,600
Aren't you being way too paranoid?

172
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,800
It's not like I'd

173
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:26,200
have some agenda with you.

174
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,920
You never know.

175
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,400
Some sex addicts

176
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,920
swing both ways.

177
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,200
I'm messing with you.

178
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:41,560
I'm not interested in women.

179
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,280
Come on. I'll take you to save A-Di.

180
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:45,920
A-Di is in danger.

181
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,360
He's in big trouble.

182
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:50,800
He went to Sis Fei's nightclub.

183
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,600
A nightclub's open for business.

184
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,400
It's not a bandit den.

185
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:55,520
Sure.

186
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,920
It's not a bandit den.

187
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,840
It's a spider demon lair.

188
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,560
Little vixens lined up,

189
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:04,040
killing without a blade,

190
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,400
using their hips instead.

191
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,120
If we don't go,

192
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,760
Sis Fei won't let him leave.

193
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:10,680
Hurry up.

194
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,480
Or those little vixens

195
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,040
will grind him down to nothing.

196
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:31,120
You two are here so early.

197
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,720
I'm not even open yet.

198
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,040
Sis Fei.

199
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,400
We're here for A-Di.

200
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,680
Once he comes out, we leave.

201
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,880
My nightclub's front door

202
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,000
isn't for just anyone to walk through.

203
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,960
You want to take A-Di away?

204
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,000
A-Di...

205
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:51,400
Since when is he your property?

206
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:54,400
He's nobody's property.

207
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:56,400
But he is my

208
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:57,480
friend.

209
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,440
Just a friend, huh.

210
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,760
Then deciding for him

211
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,480
Isn't that crossing a line?

212
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,280
If he won't go back,

213
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:07,200
that's fine,

214
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,880
but let him come out and say it.

215
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,760
Then you'll have to wait a bit.

216
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,840
Last night,

217
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:16,400
he went all night with a few girls.

218
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:17,640
Right now,

219
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,400
he's sleeping like a baby.

220
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:20,960
In that case,

221
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:22,840
we won't trouble you, Sis Fei.

222
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,840
We'll go find him ourselves.

223
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:27,120
What do you take this place for?

224
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,560
Some outsider little brat

225
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:31,320
daring to cause trouble on my turf?

226
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,280
Sis Fei, you wanna do this the hard way.

227
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:40,800
I

228
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,640
happen to like it hard.

229
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:47,600
Sis Fei, you've got power and pull.

230
00:13:47,800 --> 00:13:49,280
Forcing me to stay here,

231
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:51,600
aren't you afraid my family will find out?

232
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,960
I've checked your background.

233
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:55,480
And I

234
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:58,960
also know you've got a tough big brother.

235
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:01,400
So what?

236
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:03,880
This is Dongba.

237
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,600
The biggest fist makes the rules.

238
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:07,320
Your brother

239
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,000
can't see the future

240
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:10,920
and show up to back you up, can he?

241
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:19,080
Blackwater Shield Int'l, Op Homing.

242
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:19,760
Ms. Shen.

243
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:21,400
Your brother hired us to keep you safe.

244
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:22,400
Ma'am,

245
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:23,600
release Ms. Shen immediately,

246
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:24,720
or you'll be treated as a threat.

247
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,400
Sis Fei.

248
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:29,760
Now,

249
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,720
Whose fist is harder?

250
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,640
They're tough, sure.

251
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,720
But this

252
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,760
is my turf.

253
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,400
Going down together

254
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:43,000
is something I can still arrange.

255
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,400
Hey, hey, hey.

256
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:50,120
Wait.

257
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,520
Hey, hey, hey.

258
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,640
Calm down.

259
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,160
Everybody calm down.

260
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,240
I'm just here to have some fun.

261
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:00,840
No need to make such a big deal, right?

262
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:01,920
A-Di,

263
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,840
I helped you out of kindness,

264
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,920
but your friend here

265
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:09,320
is about to wreck my place.

266
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,160
A-Di,

267
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,000
Come with me.

268
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:13,360
It's all a misunderstanding.

269
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,680
It's all a misunderstanding.

270
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:16,680
Xingyu,

271
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:18,480
Tell them to put their guns down.

272
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:19,840
Let's go.

273
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,040
Hold it.

274
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,360
You can leave.

275
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:25,160
But her,

276
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:26,360
she stays here.

277
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:30,680
Youyou,

278
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:33,440
You haven't seen me these past few days,

279
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,240
and I didn't come looking for you either.

280
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,320
Now that we ran into each other today,

281
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,480
stay and let's have a proper talk.

282
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,320
Sis Fei,

283
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,240
So now,

284
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:57,080
are we still going down together?
